Its undirectd graph bfs dfs and adjacency list 

There is a little difference in their codes 
1. Undirected Graph

//Edge dono sides jata hai

void addEdge(int v, int w) {
    adj[v].add(w);
    adj[w].add(v);  // reverse edge bhi add hota hai
}

2. Directed Graph

// Edge sirf ek direction mein hota hai

void addEdge(int v, int w) {
    adj[v].add(w);  // sirf one side
}
